				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Philomeen is ready to die for her cause. She has run from the duergar with explosives and when the player arrives, she assumes they are a true soul and would sooner blow herself up than let the player take her to Moonrise.\r\n\r\nIf you reach the end of her dialogue, she'll leave once you get far enough away."
